        "client_msg_id": "d7415b98-1d4e-43e6-97ff-46da71376b4d",
        "type": "message",
        "text": "when it comes to choosing the type of task, i try to make it as close as possible to the work they'll be completing in the role. also consider any weaknesses or gaps in their portfolio - what do you have doubts on?\n\ni typically use a hiring scorecard that lists the different skill areas for the role, so you could use something like that as a reference as well. fill out the scorecard after the interview and then it helps you to identify those gaps that you can test with the writing assignment.",
